<h2 id="01-jquery">01. <a href="https://jquery.com/">jQuery</a></h2>
<blockquote>
  <p>Official website: <a href="https://jquery.com/">https://jquery.com/</a>
jQuery is a fast, small and feature-rich JavaScript library. Created by <a href="https://twitter.com/jeresig">John Resig</a>.</p>
</blockquote>

<p><img src="/assets/img/js/jquery.png" alt="jQuery" /></p>

