<blockquote>
  <p>Official website: <a href="http://yuilibrary.com/">http://yuilibrary.com/</a>
Created by Yahoo !, YUI is an open source JavaScript and CSS library for creating rich, interactive web applications. <a href="http://yahooeng.tumblr.com/">New updates have been stopped since August 29, 2014</a>.</p>
</blockquote>

<p><img src="/assets/img/js/yui.png" alt="YUI" /></p>

